1) Run the code corresponding to which ever cipher you wanna use
2) For encrypting a word please call the encrypt fuction by giving the word you want to encrypt as argument to the fuction
3) The cipher text will be displayed
4) For decrypting the cipher text, call the decrypt function by giving the cipher text as argumentto the fuction.
5) In case of vegenere cipher a key also have to be given as argument.
